            . The prisoner was brought to me by a neighbour, and I was informed he had stolen a cap from my son John's head - this is the cap; I know it is my son's- he had been sent to school with it, and as he came back this happened; he is six years old.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321129-194-person1736">
                  ROBERT 
                  MANN
