                     <interp inst="t18321129-194-person1736" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming along Myrtle-street, and heard the child scream; the prisoner ran towards me: I caught him - he said, "Pray, let me go," and the cap dropped from him - he said, "Allow me to go back to the child, and I will give it him."</p>
